About UsProduct Advisory Board		
Product Advisory Board


Medgate has established a product advisory board consisting of client representatives and select Medgate employees. The product advisory board was created in order to review proposed product enhancements, planned functionality for the next release, and to explore strategic direction for our product in the future. The board is divided into functional groups, medical, safety, industrial hygiene, and integrated disability management. The board is an important forum for the exchange and free flow of ideas that will help Medgate remain the leading provider of EHS software.





